page.title: 07My Interests by David Talbot
page.content:
I am David Andrew Talbot. I live at Moat Farm, Woodhouse Drive, Whitmore. I have one brother. In the week my day begins with breakfast and then I have to get ready for school.I usually go by car and stay to dinner.When I get home I usually practice my football, have tea and then a bath. I watch my video and go to bed at eight o clock. We have 3 televisions, 3 cars, one video recorder and two telephones.
My weekend includes cubs on Friday night, watching Stoke City play football on Saturday and a visit to my Nanny's.
